<doc id="1027471" wikidata="Q2349118" url="?curid=1027471" title="List of The Flintstones episodes">
<text>&quot;The Flintstones&quot; is an American animated sitcom produced by Hanna-Barbera Productions that aired on ABC from September 30, 1960 to April 1, 1966. As of September 2006, all six seasons have been released on DVD in North America. In all, 166 episodes were produced for the original series.

